import { Container, Grid } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Skills = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <Grid container
        sx={{
          position: 'relative',
          backgroundColor: 'rgb(30, 30, 30)',
          px: { md: '20px', xs: 0 },
          mt: { md: -2, xs: -5 },
          height: { xs: '80vh', md: '90vh' },
          overflow: 'hidden',
          alignItems: 'stretch',  // Make children fill container height fully
        }}>
        About section
      </Grid>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Skills
